#Linear Discriminant Analysis - Binary-class
library(MASS) 
lda_breast_canser <- lda(HER1_status ~ Protein1+Protein2+Protein3+Protein4, data=breast_canser) 
lda_breast_canser

## lda(HER1_status ~ Protein1 + Protein2 + Protein3 + Protein4,
